micropolisj.engine

Enum Sound

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Sound>
      • micropolisj.engine.Sound
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Sound>

    public enum Sound
extends java.lang.Enum<Sound>
    Enumerates the various sounds that the city may produce. The engine is not responsible for actually playing the sound. That task belongs to the front-end (i.e. the user interface).
